36:03.230 --> 36:04.331
He said, because we just put together some pieces.

36:04.351 --> 36:05.232
And he said, that book,

36:05.498 --> 36:09.024
I heard a story about the book.

36:09.044 --> 36:10.366
I'd love to hear it.

36:10.466 --> 36:14.712
Okay, it was Hartford Grace.

