40:34.705 --> 40:55.810
The typical customer will come in and buy one, is that right?

40:55.830 --> 40:56.971
They usually buy, yeah, it's not just one book at a time.

40:56.991 --> 40:58.833
The sales are generally four or five books, and sometimes 20 or 30, depending on who or not.

40:58.853 --> 40:59.855
