45:31.071 --> 45:33.656
My favorite thing at the store is putting together libraries.

45:33.796 --> 45:37.463
One person taking them apart, one person putting them together.

45:38.050 --> 45:40.777
So I do lots of libraries.

45:40.877 --> 45:45.047
I do three different kinds, basically.

45:45.067 --> 45:49.158
One is just filler books.

45:50.942 --> 45:55.333
Hi.

