46:31.543 --> 46:33.425
This is actually for decoration.

46:33.445 --> 46:34.166
Yeah, decoration.

46:34.186 --> 46:35.468
Some people it's for shoots.

46:35.488 --> 46:36.789
You know, it just depends.

