47:24.535 --> 47:25.417
That was with Laura.

47:25.437 --> 47:25.557
Yeah.

47:25.577 --> 47:26.999
I think my own age, right?

47:27.039 --> 47:27.640
Right, right, right.

47:27.957 --> 47:29.179
So it just really depends.

47:29.199 --> 47:33.847
And then, you know, if they have somebody open up a restaurant, it's more like a brewery type restaurant.

47:33.907 --> 47:35.169
We pick the older books.

47:35.309 --> 47:41.580
